{"tid":1902493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我屌哂你地老母 成個熱門都係孫楊停賽","createTime":"2020-02-28T11:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:07:19.000Z","uid":254191,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6fae633e52c45accf967a114808ebf7f2ee1f639","tid":1902493,"uid":254191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？ <br />\n做咩成個熱門都係孫楊同股票post？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死 </ins></span><br />\n連我個<span style=\"color: red;\">淺藍老母</span>都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸 <br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bba2b08bfee35e663561f21f4180e19c73a2ac","tid":1902493,"uid":254191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:12:27.000Z","msg":"冇人推依個post 你地係咪當義士係condom"},{"pid":"d5d8f8363bb3db77929b8b19e5b8966cfac3f316","tid":1902493,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"孫楊死撚左都唔關我地香港人事啦"},{"pid":"eedad498940588ba88b285af392ab2d36dab0cb3","tid":1902493,"uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"國際戰線最大敵人係「中國形象」，即係一種認為「中國屬於和平掘起，西方應該學習接納」既虛假意識。而孫楊事件背後其實正正係中國模式與人類文明既衝突，有助打破中國形象既謊言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f19c9a73d38f12cb1358a9d633155231da1e1c","tid":1902493,"uid":319616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"屌得啱<br />\n但可唔可以又係呢個template 到時用到變公廁格式 個個入到黎睇都唔睇即刻走"},{"pid":